title: My Wife is a Heavenly Big Shot
alternative_titles: 我的妻子是大乘期大佬
Wo De Qizi Shi Dacheng Qi Da Lao
My Wife is a Heavenly Big Shot
summary: My Wife is a Heavenly Big Shot Manhua Wo De Qizi Shi Dacheng Qi Da Lao 我的妻子是大乘期大佬 The opening scene mentions a wife who has reached her power ceiling, who still wants a bicycle, and demands to eat only soft rice?! But when Xiao Yifeng said I was really your husband, I was nearly strangled to death by this future wife… something’s not right, I must have taken the wrong script!
